Take the pancake mix from the refrigerator.
Add  400ml  of  milk.
Shake  the bottle  head  down  for  1  minute.  
Let  the  pancake-mix  sit for for 2-3 minutes, then shake again.
Pour the mix into the frying pan.
Wait for 3 minutes.
Flip the pancake around.
Wait for 3 minutes.
Place the pancake onto a plate.
